dct_title_s: Kort over den Vestlige Landkantas Africa fradet Hvide Forbierg til Tanit
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Bar scale statement: Maalestav af 10 Sömile.
Shows coastline, shoals, anchoring points (indicated with anchor icons).
Appears in Prévost's L'Histoire generale des voyages.
